{"word":"G5520 - χολάω - choláō - khol-ah'-o - Be angry","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">χολάω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">choláō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">khol-ah'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Be angry</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - எரிச்சலாயிரு"},{"paragraph":"1. to be atrabilious; to be mad"},{"paragraph":"2. to be angry, enraged"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5521 - χολή - cholḗ - khol-ay'/5521\">G5521</a>; to <i>be bilious</i>, that is, (by implication) <i>irritable</i> (<i>enraged</i>, &ldquo;choleric&rdquo;): - be angry.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}